            h3 Model United Nations
            h4 Today the conference, tomorrow the world.
            p. 
              Model United Nations is a student conference with the aim of bringing the negotiations and experience of a real UN conference to life.
              Academically, we not only aim to simulate the United Nations and grant our delegates the opportunity to expand their global views and leadership talents, but also cultivate a new generation of young innovators ready to become the present of the future.
