          .col-lg-10.col-md-9.col-8#twmun_discription
            h3 "Taiwan" Model United Nations
            h4 We came, we saw, we TWMUN.
            p.
              TWMUN is co-founded by National Chiao Tung University MUN and National Tsing Hua University MUN, and is also meant to symbolize a close cooperation between the two schools in the realm of international affairs.
              Undergraduate and graduate students gather for three days to discuss, debate, and to solve a variety of current global and local issues. TWMUN brings annually special committees to expand the learning horizons of our delegates.

